 state-of-the-art facilities – with stringent quality-controls that ensure your finished product arrives on time and satisfies your exacting standards.    \r\n<br /><br />\r\n<h3 class=\"heading\">Customize Your Supplement’s Ingredients</h3>\r\nNPI helps you design and formulate your supplements with the hottest ingredients & newest dosage designs in the dynamic nutritional product marketplace. Our highly-skilled formulators work in state-of-the-art labs with our trusted network of material suppliers, expert technicians & product developers to make your vision a reality.\r\n\r\nNPI has a huge range of globally-sourced raw materials at our disposal – so whether you’re looking to develop & manufacture a brand-new product, improve your existing supplement line, or reverse-engineer an existing product our chemists and engineers are standing by.\r\n\r\nInnovation moves quickly at NPI. We have a small-batch product-pilot development process – making it easy to ramp up production as soon as your product is ready for market. This allows your supplement formula to move through the development cycle with incredible speed and precision – from concept to commercialization.    \r\n</p>\r\n</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2014-02-14 13:49:24','2014-02-14 13:49:24','howitwork','*'),(1010,'detail_partial',472,3,'<%= render :inline=>this.init %>\r\n<style>\r\n.orderdetail {\r\n    \r\n	border:1px solid #ccc; background:FFFFAE;\r\n-moz-border-radius: 5px;\r\nborder-radius: 5px;\r\n-moz-box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #ccc;\r\n-webkit-box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #ccc;\r\nbox-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #ccc;\r\nfont-size:1em;\r\npadding:5px;\r\n	}    \r\n    \r\n</style>\r\n<%\r\n@products = []\r\ncat_count = {}\r\n\r\n  if @item\r\n   if @categories\r\n   @products = @product_model.where(:category=>{\'$in\'=>@categories.collect{|i| i.id}})\r\n   end\r\n\r\n  \r\n  map = {}\r\n  \r\n  \r\n if @formula_items\r\n @products.each do |i| \r\n   map[i._id]=i\r\n end\r\n end\r\n  \r\n  \r\n%>\r\n<%\r\n\r\n\r\n   if requ